## ğŸš€ Project Overview

Managing emails becomes inefficient when conversations grow long and complex.  
The **Email Triage Assistant** uses AI agents to analyze email content, compress conversations, classify messages, and suggest appropriate responses.

This project focuses on **context-aware automation** to help users read less and respond faster.

